    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - INSTALL - DETENT SPRING
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>DETENT SPRING</title>
        <figure id="f13032g9" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg13/G13032g9.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 169. Detent Spring Assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f13032g9">Figure 169</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the detent spring(s) and detent plunger in the shift block.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the shift block on the shift shaft using the following procedure.</para>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Tilt the shift block so the plunger faces slightly upward.</para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Place the plunger in the center of the detent notch, and press the detent plunger in to
                    compress the detent springs.
                </para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">While the springs are compressed, roll the shift block into place on the shift shaft. If
                    the shift shaft has been moved or otherwise disturbed, it may be necessary to slide the shift shaft
                    fore or aft to properly install the shift block (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f13032h0">Figure 170</hotlnk>).
                </para>
            </step2>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the socket head bolt to secure the shift block. Tighten the bolt to 54 to 61 Nm (40
                to 45 ft-lbs) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13032h1">Figure 171</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13032h0" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg13/G13032h0.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 170. Roll Shift Block into Place</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f13032h1" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg13/G13032h1.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 171. Install Socket Head Bolt</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
